<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Khuy%E1%BA%BFn/author-JHbQVfC53E2lRJL-xE616A">Nguyễn Khuyến</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Khuy%E1%BA%BFn/Ng%E1%BA%ABu-th%C3%A0nh-k%E1%BB%B3-4/poem-1G-ZjqcGwVRfA4XsdGDQhQ">Ngẫu thành kỳ 4 - 偶城其四</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Khuy%E1%BA%BFn/author-JHbQVfC53E2lRJL-xE616A">Nguyễn Khuyến</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Thu%E1%BB%B3-b%E1%BA%A1ch/poem-w7DEiYB3UzHtOCSifKigrQ">Thuỳ bạch - 垂白</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%E1%BB%97-T%E1%BA%A5n/T%C3%ADch-hoa-b%E1%BB%99-T%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Ch%C3%A2u-T%C3%A0ng-Xu%C3%A2n-vi%C3%AAn-ch%E1%BB%A7-nh%C3%A2n-nguy%C3%AAn-v%E1%BA%ADn-k%E1%BB%B3-4/poem-S6C3Yi81DyJSK-jCA8DKcw">Tích hoa bộ Tương Châu Tàng Xuân viên chủ nhân nguyên vận kỳ 4 - 惜花步藏湘州春園主人元韻其四</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%E1%BB%97-T%E1%BA%A5n/author-TXAaCmjdRWIV6MkCYE1psQ">Lỗ Tấn</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Cao-B%C3%A1-Qu%C3%A1t/V%E1%BB%8Bnh-T%E1%BA%A3n-Vi%C3%AAn-s%C6%A1n/poem-GHFcjRgVOl9L-rxRem9TjA">Vịnh Tản Viên sơn - 詠傘園山</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Cao-B%C3%A1-Qu%C3%A1t/author-2eyz08Vw3mwjAHFJik43sA">Cao Bá Quát</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
